One way you could say is
if you buy no chocolate,

00:09:26.997 --> 00:09:28.466
if the quantity of chocolate is 0,

00:09:28.466 --> 00:09:30.800
what is going to be the quantity of fruit?

00:09:30.800 --> 00:09:33.058
Then you could solve this
or you could just say,

00:09:33.058 --> 00:09:34.059
"Look, if I have $20 a month

